Nitpick:
I personally think the method should not accept null lists. Just add a javadoc that has "@param list never null"

But if should accept null too, we treat is as an exceptionally situation (so handle it with an if statement before doing the real code)
```

if (list == null) {
   return "";
}
String abbreviation = ...
```

